%3ELast%20month%2C%20Canadian%20prime%20minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20had%20said%20in%20the%20lower%20house%20of%20parliament%20that%20there%20were%20%E2%80%9Ccredible%20allegations%E2%80%9D%20of%20a%20potential%20link%20between%20Indian%20government%20agents%20and%20the%20shooting%20of%20Canadian%20Sikh%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20who%20is%20described%20as%20a%20terrorist%20by%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.abc.net.au%2Fnews%2F2023-10-19%2Fasio-chief-says-no-reason-to-dispute-canada-india-spy-claim%2F102993480%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20Australia%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EABC%20New%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Es%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Australia%20Security%20Intelligence%20Organisation%20(ASIO)%20director%20general%20Mike%20Burgess%20was%20asked%20about%20his%20assessment%20of%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20allegations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20have%20no%20reason%20to%20dispute%20what%20the%20Canadian%20government%20has%20said%20in%20this%20matter%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20replied.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20had%20dismissed%20the%20allegations%20as%20%E2%80%9Cbiased%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cmotivated%E2%80%9D%2C%20reiterating%20that%20Canada%20never%20taken%20Indian%20concerns%20on%20activities%20of%20pro-Khalistani%20groups%20seriously.%20After%20Canada%20expelled%20a%20senior%20Indian%20diplomat%2C%20India%20did%20the%20same%20to%20a%20Canadian%20diplomat.%20India%20also%20suspended%20visa%20operations%20for%20Canadian%20nationals%20and%20also%20called%20on%20Canada%20to%20downsize%20its%20diplomatic%20missions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20US%20ambassador%20to%20Canada%20David%20Cohen%20had%20explicitly%20linked%20the%20Canadian%20accusation%20to%20the%20five%20eyes%20intelligence%20network.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20shared%20intelligence%20among%20Five%20Eyes%20partners%20that%20helped%20lead%20Canada%20to%20making%20the%20statements%20that%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20made%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20in%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fshared-intelligence-of-five-eye-partners-informed-trudeaus-allegations-says-us-envoy-to-canada%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Einterview%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20CTV%20News%2C%20a%20Canadian%20news%20channel.%20The%20US%20has%20repeatedly%20asked%20India%20to%20join%20the%20Canadian%20investigations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAustralia%20is%20also%20member%20of%20the%20Five%20Eyes%20network%20which%20is%20an%20intelligence-sharing%20alliance%20that%20also%20includes%20the%20United%20States%2C%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20Canada%20and%20New%20Zealand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ASIO%20chief%20also%20echoed%20the%20Australian%20reaction%20that%20the%20allegations%20made%20by%20Canada%20were%20serious.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20no%20doubt%20any%20allegation%20of%20any%20country%20being%20accused%20of%20carrying%20out%20an%20execution%20of%20a%20citizen%20in%20that%20country%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20serious%20allegation%2C%20and%20something%20that%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20do%20and%20something%20that%20nations%20should%20not%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20interview%20took%20place%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20Five%20Eyes%20summit%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EABC%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20report%2C%20Burgess%20did%20not%20confirm%20whether%20the%20India%20issue%20was%20discussed%20at%20the%20summit.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20asked%20whether%20Australian%20Sikhs%20could%20be%20next%20target%20for%20Indian%20agents%2C%20Burgess%20answered%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20job%20is%20to%20look%20for%20espionage%20and%20foreign%20interference.%20When%20we%20find%20it%2C%20we%20deal%20with%20it%20effectively.%20Whether%20or%20not%20it%20will%20happen%20here%2C%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20publicly%20speculate%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20that%E2%80%99s%20appropriate.%20I%20can%20assure%20you%20that%20when%20we%20find%20governments%20interfering%20in%20our%20country%2C%20or%20planning%20to%20interfere%20in%20our%20country%2C%20we%20will%20deal%20with%20them%20effectively%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20observed%20that%20%E2%80%9Cmultiple%20countries%E2%80%9D%20had%20tried%20to%20interfere%20in%20Australian%20society%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Faustralia-news%2F2023%2Ffeb%2F14%2Faustralia-foils-iran-surveillance-plot-and-vows-to-bring-foreign-interference-into-the-light%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eciting%20Iran%E2%80%99s%20attempt%20to%20target%20an%20Iranian-Australian%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ASIO%20head%20noted%20that%20in%20multi-cultural%20societies%2C%20there%20are%20often%20tensions%20associated%20from%20their%20home%20countries%20which%20find%20resonance%20in%20the%20diaspora.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20us%2C%20that%20plays%20out%20in%20society%2C%20you%20see%20protests%2C%20counter-protests%2C%20and%20sometimes%20there%E2%80%99s%20communal%20violence%20or%20spontaneous%20violence.%20That%E2%80%99s%20not%20a%20nation%20state%20seeking%20to%20interfere%20and%20covertly%20or%20deceptively%20harm%20and%20intimidate%20people.%20Of%20course%2C%20if%20we%20see%20that%2C%20we%20will%20act%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697720646000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19182259%2FScreenshot-2023-10-19-at-6.22.52%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Faustralia-spy-chief-mike-burgess-canada-nijjar-india-five-eyes%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20an%20intervie