ouncement%20that%20Israel%20has%20agreed%20to%20permit%20humanitarian%20aid%20for%20Gaza%20through%20the%20Rafah%20crossing%20in%20Egypt%2C%20Sarna%20pointed%20out%20that%20this%20will%20be%20heavily%20impacted%20by%20the%20conditions%20Israel%20has%20laid%20down.%20Those%20conditions%20not%20only%20require%20checking%20of%20the%20trucks%20coming%20into%20Gaza%20by%20the%20Red%20Cross%20and%20not%20sharing%20the%20supplies%20with%20Hamas%20but%20also%20rule%20out%20the%20supply%20of%20fuel%20and%2C%20additionally%2C%20limit%20the%20supplies%20to%20only%20south%20Gaza%20and%20not%20Gaza%20north%20of%20Wadi%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20BBC%2C%20there%20are%20still%20some%204-500%2C000%20Palestinians%20in%20north%20Gaza%20and%20they%2C%20therefore%2C%20will%20not%20get%20access%20to%20these%20supplies.%20Also%2C%20it%20seems%2C%20only%2020%20trucks%20will%20be%20permitted%20entry%20into%20Gaza%20on%20Friday.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20will%20happen%20thereafter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20many%20other%20issues%20raised%20with%20Sarna%20in%20this%20interview.%20This%20includes%20the%20cancellation%20of%20the%20Jordan%20summit%20and%2C%20also%2C%20a%20question%20of%20whether%20President%20Biden%20and%20the%20United%20States%E2%80%99s%20endorsement%20of%20the%20Israeli%20position%20that%20Islamic%20jihad%20was%20responsible%20for%20the%20attack%20on%20the%20Gaza%20hospital%20will%20upset%20or%2C%20at%20least%2C%20be%20of%20great%20concern%20to%20the%20Arab%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20questions%20about%20whether%20President%20Biden%E2%80%99s%20personal%20and%20emotional%20behaviour%20in%20clear%20support%20of%20Israel%20will%20have%20an%20impact%20on%20the%20Arab%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EQuestions%20are%20also%20asked%20about%20whether%20the%20last%2011%20days%20have%20created%20an%20opportunity%20or%2C%20at%20least%2C%20room%20for%20China%20to%20fish%20in%20Middle%20Eastern%20waters.%20After%20successfully