20land%2C%20their%20sufferings%20are%20deep-rooted%20and%20grievances%20long.%20Their%20aspirations%20to%20retrieve%20what%20they%20lost%20and%20to%20have%20a%20country%20of%20their%20own%20minus%20the%20indignities%20they%20currently%20suffer%20under%20the%20Israeli%20occupation%20are%20also%20real.%20No%20amount%20of%20Israeli%20coercive%20tactics%20will%20ever%20be%20enough%20to%20push%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20to%20give%20up%20on%20their%20collective%20dreams.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20that%20matter%2C%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20this%20time%20highlighted%20the%20shortcomings%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20strongarm%20policies.%20It%20has%20been%20years%20now%20that%20Israel%20has%20been%20attempting%20to%20choke%20Gaza%2C%20making%20periodic%20incursions%20into%20the%20strip%20that%20it%20has%20kept%20under%20tight%20siege%20to%20finish%20off%20the%20armed%20group.%20It%20has%20killed%20Hamas%20leaders%20and%20fighters%20in%20hundreds%20and%20targeted%20incessantly%20their%20labyrinth%20of%20supply%20tunnels%20that%20the%20group%20uses%20to%20arm%20itself.%20Yet%2C%20the%20Hamas%20survived%20and%20managed%20to%20spring%20a%20surprise%20by%20launching%20what%20was%20its%20biggest%20cross-border%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EClearly%2C%20Palestinian%20armed%20opposition%20will%20continue%20in%20some%20form%20or%20another%20as%20long%20as%20Israel%20lets%20the%20root%20causes%20%E2%80%93%20issues%20such%20as%20Palestinian%20statehood%20and%20the%20right%20of%20Palestinians%20to%20a%20dignified%20life%20%E2%80%93%20to%20fester%20unattended.%20Taking%20on%20mere%20symptoms%20such%20as%20Hamas%20may%20yield%20temporary%20results%2C%20but%20will%20do%20little%20to%20solve%20the%20long-standing%20problem%20permanently.%20As%20a%20matter%20of%20fact%2C%20Israeli%20intransigence%20remains%20the%20perfect%20incubator%20for%20an%20armed%20resistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFortunately%2C%20just%20as%20not%20every%20Gazan%20is%20a%20Hamas%20supporter%2C%20not%20every%20Israeli%20is%