20with%20intermittent%20Israeli%20army%20checkpoints%20under%20whose%20noses%20Israeli%20settlers%20have%20been%20grabbing%20more%20Palestinian%20land%20and%20setting%20up%20newer%20settlements.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAngrier%20Palestinians%2C%20post%20the%20current%20phase%20of%20death%20and%20destruction%2C%20pose%20greater%20problems%20for%20Israel.%20Their%20grievances%20unattended%2C%20Palestinians%20will%20look%20to%20vent%20their%20frustrations%20in%20whichever%20way%20possible.%20Even%20if%20Hamas%20ceases%20to%20exist%20as%20a%20potent%20armed%20group%2C%20there%20will%20be%20no%20dearth%20of%20hot-heads%20among%20Palestinian%20ranks%20who%20would%20seek%20to%20harm%20Israelis%20wherever%20they%20live%20%E2%80%93%20in%20Israel%20or%20elsewhere.%20Instead%20of%20pummelling%20them%20into%20submission%2C%20Israel%20by%20its%20indiscriminate%20attack%20on%20Gaza%20may%20have%20accentuated%20the%20problem%20by%20provoking%20and%20converting%20more%20Palestinians%20into%20hardliners.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20something%20that%20the%20Israelis%20themselves%20would%20come%20to%20realise%20once%20the%20dust%20in%20Gaza%20settles%20and%20the%20deceptive%20calm%20returns.%20By%20far%20the%20greatest%20military%20strength%20in%20the%20region%2C%20its%20fabled%20security%20apparatus%20failed%20miserably%20against%20ingenious%20Palestinians%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20paraglided%20into%20Israeli%20territory%20to%20kill%20its%20citizens.%20It%20could%20fail%20in%20the%20future%20too%20%E2%80%93%20both%20in%20Israel%20and%20abroad%20%E2%80%93%20if%20the%20Palestinian%20problem%20is%20to%20persist.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBy%20all%20accounts%2C%20the%20latest%20mayhem%20will%20end%20up%20mainstreaming%20the%20Palestinian%20cause%20that%20otherwise%20seemed%20to%20be%20meandering%20minus%20much%20resonance%20in%20the%20recent%20past.%20Aided%20by%20its%20friends%20in%20the%20West%2C%20Israel%20had%20been%20ignoring%20it%20at%20its%20own%20peril.%20Even%20neighbouring%20Arab%20states