https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104557108.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EJunaid%20Khan%2C%20son%20of%20actor%20Aamir%20Khan%2C%20is%20preparing%20to%20make%20his%20screen%20debut%20with%20Yash%20Raj%20Films'%20Maharaj%20after%20years%20of%20work%20in%20theatre.%20His%20recent%20photoshoot%20by%20Avinash%20Gowariker%20has%20garnered%20attention%2C%20with%20fans%20commenting%20on%20his%20transformation.%20Junaid%20has%20been%20following%20his%20passion%20for%20acting%2C%20starting%20with%20theatre%20in%202017%2C%20and%20is%20now%20ready%20to%20make%20his%20mark%20on%20the%20big%20screen.%20In%20addition%20to%20Maharaj%2C%20he%20is%20also%20set%20to%20produce%20a%20film%20titled%20%26quot%3BPritam%20Pyaare.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Faamir-khans-son-junaid-khan-looks-unrecognisable-in-his-latest-photoshoot%2Farticleshow%2F104557108.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BDifficult%20To%20Evacuate%20Indians%20From%20Gaza%20Now%26quot%3B%3A%20Centre%20On%20Israel-Hamas%20War%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20four%20Indians%20in%20Gaza%20and%20the%20situation%20is%20not%20conducive%20for%20an%20evacuation%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20will%20be%20repatriated%20at%20the%20first%20opportunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20situation%20in%20Gaza%20is%20difficult%20for%20any%20evacuation%20but%20if%20we%20get%20a%20chance%2C%20we%20will%20get%20them%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20MEA%20spokesperson%20Arindam%20Bagchi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20them%20is%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20no%20reports%20of%20any%20Indian%20being%20killed%20or%20injured%20in%20Gaza%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bstrongly%20condemning%26quot%3B%20the%20terror%20attack%20on%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20Indian%2C%20a%20caregiver%20in%20south%20Israel's%20Ashkelon%2C%20was%20injured%20in%20the%20war%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas.%20She%20was%20on%20a%20video%20call%20with%20her%20husband%20when%20a%20barrage%20of%20Hamas%20rockets%20pounded%20Israel%20on%20October%207%2C%20a%20day%20of%20Sabbath%20and%20a%20Jewish%20holiday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20expressed%20concerns%20over%20civilian%20casualties%20and%20the%20humanitarian%20situation%2C%20Mr%20Bachi%20said%2C%20speaking%20about%20the%20horrific%20airstrike%20on%20a%20hospital%20in%20Gaza%20that%20has%20killed%20over%20500.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20seen%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20tweet.%20PM%20has%20expressed%20his%20concern%20over%20the%20death%20of%20civilians%20and%20extended%20his%20condolences%20to%20the%20families.%20India%20condemns%20all%20forms%20of%20violence%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BOn%20the%20Palestine%20issue%2C%20we%20have%20reiterated%20our%20position%20in%20favour%20of%20direct%20negotiations%20for%20a%20two-state%20solution.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20MEA%20spokesperson%20also%20urged%20the%20international%20community%20to%20come%20together%20to%20combat%20terrorism%20in%20all%20its%20forms.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAir%20strikes%20on%20a%20hospital%20compound%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20late%20Monday%20night%20killed%20at%20least%20500%20people%2C%20officials%20in%20the%20Hamas-run%20Palestinian%20territory%20said.%20It%20blamed%20Israel%20for%20the%20strike%2C%20sparking%20widespread%20condemnation%20and%20fury.%20However%2C%20Israel%20denied%20any%20involvement%2C%20calling%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bmisfire%26quot%3B%20by%20Hamas%2C%20and%20subsequently%20released%20a%20host%20of%20satellite%20pics%20and%20%26quot%3Bbefore-after%26quot%3B%20footage%20of%20the%20hospital%20bombing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20repatriated%201%2C200%20people%20from%20Israel%2C%20includi