godrej-capital-eyes-rs-10-000-cr-aum-by-march-hit-rs-50-000-cr-by-2028-123101900734_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fgodrej-capital-eyes-rs-10-000-cr-aum-by-march-hit-rs-50-000-cr-by-2028-123101900734_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fgodrej-capital-eyes-rs-10-000-cr-aum-by-march-hit-rs-50-000-cr-by-2028-123101900734_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Over%201%2C000%20Himachal%20Cops%20Fell%20Victim%20To%20Cryptocurrency%20Fraud%3A%20Officials%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOver%20a%20thousand%20police%20personnel%20fell%20victim%20to%20a%20fake%20local%20cryptocurrency%20created%20by%20fraudsters%20in%20Himachal's%20Mandi%20district%2C%20an%20official%20said%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20majority%20of%20the%20police%20personnel%20who%20invested%20in%20the%20fake%20cryptocurrency%20were%20duped%20of%20crores%20of%20rupees%2C%20but%20some%20of%20them%20made%20huge%20gains%2C%20became%20promoters%20of%20the%20scheme%2C%20and%20roped%20in%20more%20investors%20for%20it%2C%20according%20to%20investigators%20of%20the%20Special%20Investigation%20Team%20(SIT)%20constituted%20to%20probe%20the%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20police%2C%20at%20least%20one%20lakh%20people%20have%20been%20duped%20by%20the%20fraudsters%20in%20the%20cryptocurrency%20fraud%2C%20and%202.5%20lakh%20IDs%20have%20been%20found%20%E2%80%93%20which%20included%20multiple%20IDs%20of%20the%20same%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20get%20investors%2C%20the%20scammers%20launched%20two%20cryptocurrencies%20%E2%80%93%20'Korvio%20Coin'%20(or%20KRO)%20and%20%E2%80%98DGT%20Coin'%20%E2%80%93%20and%20created%20fake%20websites%20with%20manipulated%20prices%20of%20these%20digital%20currencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20lured%20the%20initial%20investors%20by%20promising%20them%20high%20returns%20in%20a%20short%20span%20of%20time.%20They%20also%20created%20a%20network%20of%20investors%2C%20who%20further%20expanded%20the%20chain%20within%20their%20own%20circles.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPolicemen%2C%20teachers%20and%20others%20got%20involved%20in%20the%20scheme%20for%20quick%20returns.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20police%20personnel%20involved%20suffered%20losses%2C%20their%20promotion%20of%20the%20scheme%20created%20trust%20among%20the%20investors%20and%20gave%20credibility%20to%20the%20investment%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESome%20policemen%20involved%20in%20the%20cryptocurrency%20scheme%20opted%20for%20voluntary%20retirement%20scheme%20(VRS)%2C%20and%20became%20its%20promoters%2C%20a%20police%20official%20told%20PTI%20on%20Thursday%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20get%20all%20the%20wrongdoers%E2%80%A6%20The%20investigation%20is%20progressing%20in%20an%20organised%20and%20planned%20manner%2C%E2%80%9D%20DGP%20Sanjay%20Kundu%20said.%20He%20added%20that%20all%20those%20involved%20in%20the%20scam%20will%20be%20dealt%20with%20strongly%20as%20per%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECryptocurrency%20is%20a%20digital%20currency%20designed%20to%20work%20as%20a%20medium%20of%20exchange%20through%20a%20blockchain-based%20computer%20network%20that%20is%20not%20dependent%20on%20any%20central%20authority%2C%20such%20as%20the%20government%20or%20bank%20to%20uphold%20or%20maintain%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20scam%20started%20in%202018%2C%20with%20a%20majority%20of%20victims%20from%20Mandi%2C%20Hamirpur%20and%20Kangra%20districts.%20In%20certain%20cases%2C%20a%20single%20person%20roped%20in%20up%20to%201%2C000%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20used%20a%20combination%20of%20misinformation%2C%20deception%20and%20threats%20to%20maintain%20control%20over%20their%20scheme%20and%20continue%20extracting%20money%20from%20unsuspecting%20investors%20by%20manipulating%20the%20cryptocurrency%20prices%20which%20led%20to%20huge%20financial%20losses%20to%20the%20victims%2C%20the%20police%20had%20earlier%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20cryptocurrency%20scammers%20approached%20people%20with%20an%20investment%20plan%20related%20to%20a%20locally%20made%20cryptocurrency%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98Korvio%20Coin'%20or%20KRO%20coins%2C%20and%20charged%20an%20initial%20activation%20fee%20for%20getting%20their%20accounts%20activated.%20Three%20to%20four%20kinds%20of%20cryptocurrency%20were%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20scammers%20built%20fake%20websites%20to%20list%20their%20coins%20and%20manipulated%20their%20prices.%20Later%2C%20they%20launched%20a%20new%20coin%20called%20'DGT%20Coin.'%20After%20enough%20people%20had%20purchased%20these%20coins%20at%20a%20higher%20rate%2C%20its%20price%20was%20deliberately%20brought%20down%20causing%20massive%20financial%20losses%20to%20the%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation%20also%20revealed%20that%20apart%20from%20cryptocurrency%2C%20other%20deposit%20schemes%2C%20such%20as%20a%2010%20per%20cent%20monthly%20return%20on%20a%20Rs%2090%2C000%20deposit%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPolice%20have%20cautioned%20the%20general%20public%20to%20be%20careful%20if%20any%20scheme%20promises%20over%2012%20per%20cent%20annual%20returns.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETwo%20main%20accused%20Sukhdev%20and%20Hemraj%2C%20who%20were%20earlier%20in%20the%20month%20arrested%20from%20Gujarat%2C%20confessed%20during%20interrogation%20that%20they%20have%20outstanding%20liabilities%20of%20Rs%20400%20crore.%20The%20alleged%20kingpin%20of%20the%20scam%2C%20Subash%2C%20is%20still%20at%20large.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697716860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-03%2Fvn2475a8_crypto-generic-cryptocurrency-generic_625x300_01_March_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-