%20the%20international%20open%20access%20Andrology%20journal%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20open-labelled%20and%20non-randomized%2C%20multi-centre%20hospital-based%20phase-III%20clinical%20trials%20were%20carried%20out%20at%20five%20different%20centres%20(New%20Delhi%2C%20Udhampur%2C%20Ludhiana%2C%20Jaipur%20and%20Kharagpur)%20and%20coordinated%20by%20the%20ICMR%2C%20New%20Delhi.%C2%A0%20Permission%20to%20conduct%20phase-III%20clinical%20trial%20was%20granted%20by%20the%20Drugs%20Controller%20General%20India%20(DCGI)%20and%20approved%20by%20the%20institutional%20ethical%20committees%20of%20the%20respective%20centres.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20study%2C%20303%20healthy%2C%20sexually%20active%20and%20married%20men%20and%20their%20healthy%20and%20sexually%20active%20wives%20who%20came%20to%20the%20family%20planning%20clinic%20and%20department%20of%20urology%20or%20surgery%20for%20vasectomy%20or%20No%20Scalpel%20Vasectomy%20(NSV)%20were%20identified.%C2%A0%20The%20men%20were%20injected%20with%2060%20mg%20of%20Reversible%20Inhibition%20of%20Sperm%20under%20Guidance%20(RISUG).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20overall%20efficacy%20of%20RISUG%20with%20respect%20to%20achieving%20azoospermia%20was%2097.3%20per%20cent%20and%20based%20on%20pregnancy%20prevention%20was%2099.02%20per%20cent%20without%20any%20serious%20side%20effect%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20study%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20history%20of%20contraceptive%20development%2C%20RISUG%20presents%20the%20highest%20effectiveness%20compared%20to%20all%20other%20contraceptives%20both%20male%20and%20female%20as%20they%20were%20at%20the%20threshold%20of%20induction%20into%20a%20mass%20contraception%20program%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20study%2C%20with%20an%20ever-increasing%20world%20population%2C%20there%20is%20an%20urgent%20need%20to%20develop%20modern%20methods%20of%20male%20contraception%20for%20population%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20vasectomy%20is%20quite%20effective%20as%20a%20contraceptive%20measure%2C%20some%20major%20limitations%20of%20this%20method%20call%20for%20the%20development%20of%20improved%20techniques.%20An%20ideal%20male%20contraceptive%20approach%20should%20have%20minimally%20invasive%20drug%20delivery%20system%20with%20a%20one-time%20injection%2C%20long-term%20effectiveness%20with%20negligible%20side-effects%20and%20the%20option%20of%20reversal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20achieve%20these%20goals%2C%20a%20novel%20male%20contraceptive%20approach%20of%20Reversible%20Inhibition%20of%20Sperm%20under%20Guidance%20(RISUG)%20has%20been%20developed%2C%20which%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20become%20for%20mass%20use%20as%20once%20injectable%20and%20reversible%20male%20contraceptive%20method.%20Significant%20features%20of%20this%20method%20include%20localized%20injection%20and%20no%20detectable%20interaction%20with%20other%20body%20parts%20unlike%20the%20hormonal%20injectable%20contraceptives%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20study%20said.%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697715900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F85g4hu6_medical-lab-generic_625x300_02_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-completes-clinical-trials-of-worlds-first-injectable-male-contraceptive-report-4495976%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research%20(ICMR)%20has%20completed%20the%20clinical%20trials%20of%20the%20world's%20first%20injectable%20male%20contraceptive%20which%20showed%20that%20it%20is%20safe%20and%20highly%20efficacious%20without%20any%20serious%20side%20effects.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-completes-