t%20diplomatic%20event%20this%20week%20-%20a%20summit%20to%20celebrate%20the%20belt%20and%20road%20(BRI)%20project%2C%20a%20multibillion-dollar%20infrastructure%20project.%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20opened%20the%20ceremony%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20several%20world%20leaders%20and%20more%20than%201%2C000%20delegates%20at%20the%20Great%20Hall%20of%20the%20People%20in%20Beijing%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20and%20shared%20the%20stage%20with%20Vladimir%20Putin%2C%20who%20made%20a%20rare%20trip%20outside%20Russia%20-%20his%20first%20this%20year.%20But%20just%20before%20Mr%20Putin's%20speech%2C%20a%20number%20of%20people%2C%20including%20European%20delegates%2C%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmong%20those%20delegates%20was%20European%20Jean-Pierre%20Raffarin%2C%20former%20prime%20minister%20of%20France%2C%20news%20agency%20Reuters%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffr_schaeffer%2Fstatus%2F1714476199861243942%5C%22%3EVideos%20from%20the%20event%3C%2Fa%3E%20show%20Mr%20Raffarin%20and%20other%20delegates%20leaving%20the%20Great%20Hall%20as%20Mr%20Putin%20was%20set%20to%20deliver%20his%20remarks%20after%20Mr%20Xi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20clips%20also%20showed%20Mr%20Putin%2C%20accompanied%20by%20his%20aides%2C%20carrying%20the%20so-called%20nuclear%20briefcase%2C%20which%20can%20be%20used%20to%20order%20a%20nuclear%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20speech%2C%20Mr%20Putin%20thanked%20the%20Chinese%20leader%20for%20his%20invitation%20and%20said%20Russia%20could%20play%20a%20key%20role%20in%20China's%20modern%20day%20revival%20of%20the%20ancient%20Silk%20Road.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRussia%20and%20China%2C%20like%20most%20countries%20of%20the%20world%2C%20share%20the%20desire%20for%20equal%2C%20mutually%20beneficial%20cooperation%20in%20order%20to%20achieve%20universal%20sustainable%20and%20long-term%20economic%20progress%20and%20social%20well-being%2C%20while%20respecting%20the%20diversity%