The%20opening%20day%20box%20office%20collection%20of%20Vijay%20and%20Lokesh%20Kanagaraj's%20film%20is%20set%20to%20become%20a%20highest%20number%20for%20a%20Tamil%20film.%20'Leo'%20is%20predicted%20to%20earn%20over%20Rs%20120%20crore%20on%20day%201.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22etimes.in%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Ftamil%2Fmovies%2Fbox-office%2Fleo-box-office-collection-day-1-vijays-action-drama-with-lokesh-kanagaraj-is-sealed-to-become-the-highest-grossing-tamil-film-of-all-time-on-the-opening-day-%2Farticleshow%2F104551042.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22On%20Gandhi%20Siblings'%20Dynasty%20Charge%2C%20A%20Reply%20From%20KCR's%20Son%20And%20Daughter%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHitting%20out%20at%20the%20Gandhi%20siblings%20over%20their%20dynasty%20charge%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20Telangana%20polls%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20K%20Chandrashekar's%20minister%20son%20and%20MLC%20daughter%20have%20said%20it%20is%20funny%20when%20great-grandchildren%20of%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20and%20grandchildren%20of%20Indira%20Gandhi%20speak%20about%20%26quot%3Bfamily%20politics%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20launched%20a%20high-voltage%20campaign%20to%20unseat%20the%20ruling%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20in%20the%20November%2030%20Assembly%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETop%20leaders%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20are%20holding%20rallies%20and%20roadshows%20in%20the%20poll-bound%20state%20and%20targeting%20BRS%20chief%20and%20Chief%20Minister%20KCR.%20Their%20verbal%20attacks%20have%20sparked%20fiery%20responses%20from%20Telangana%20minister%20and%20KCR's%20son%20KT%20Rama%20Rao%20and%20his%20sister%20and%20Legislative%20Council%20member%20K%20Kavitha.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20Ms%20Gandhi%20Vadra's%20remarks%20on%20accommodating%20family%20members%20in%20the%20cabinet%2C%20Ms%20Kavitha%20said%20%26quot%3Bpeople%20who%20live%20in%20glass%20houses%20shouldn't%20throw%20stones%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPriyanka%20Gandhi%20ji%2C%20the%20great-great-granddaughter%20of%20Motilal%20Nehru%20ji%2C%20great-granddaughter%20of%20Jawahar%20Lal%20Nehru%20ji%2C%20granddaughter%20of%20Indira%20Gandhi%20ji%20and%20daughter%20of%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20ji%2C%20is%20talking%20about%20family%20politics.%20This%20is%20the%20funniest%20thing%20I%20have%20heard%20in%20the%20whole%20election%20campaign%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20reporters%20in%20Armoor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMs%20Kavitha%20has%20also%20hit%20out%20at%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20saying%20he%20can%20visit%20Telangana%20as%20a%20tourist%2C%20enjoy%20its%20delicacy%20Ankapur%20chicken%20and%20go%20back.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20no%20place%20in%20Telangana.%20That%20is%20why%20Mr%20Rahul%20ji%20we%20want%20to%20call%20you%20only%20Election%20Gandhi%20not%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%20This%20(name%20Rahul%20Gandhi)%20does%20not%20suit%20you%20when%20you%20come%20to%20Telangana.%20When%20you%20come%20to%20Nizamabad%2C%20have%20Ankapur%20chicken%2C%20which%20is%20very%20popular%20here.%20We%20welcome%20you%20to%20come%20here%20as%20a%20tourist%20and%20please%20go.%20Thank%20you%20so%20much%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20reporters%20in%20Bodhan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20rally%20in%20Mulugu%2C%20Ms%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20had%20slammed%20the%20KCR%20government%2C%20saying%20the%20people%20of%20Telangana%20had%20dreamt%20of%20social%20justice%2C%20but%20three%20ministers%20are%20from%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F58lbd0ag_rahul-gandhi-telangana_625x300_19_October_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EHer%20brother%20and%20MP%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20too%2C%20has%20targeted%20KCR%20over%20dynasty%20politics.%20At%20a%20roadshow%20in%20Bhupalpally%20today%2C%20he%20said%20the%20people%20of%20Telangana%2C%20who%20had%20joined%20the%20statehood%20movement%2C%20had%20dreamt%20of%20a%20state%20where%20the%20common%20man%20would%20govern.%20%26quot%3BBut%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20your%20Chief%20Minister%20KCR%20has%20distanced%20himself%20from%20the%20people%2C%20and%20only%20his%20family%20is%20ruling%20the%20state.%20He%20has%20shattered%20your%20dream%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Mr%20Gandhi%20also%20said%20this%20is%20a%C2%A0%26quot%3BDorala%20Telangana%20(feudal%20lords)%20vs%20Prajala%20Telangana%20(common%20people)%26quot%3B%20fight%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20sharp%20response%20to%20the%20dynasty%20charge%2C%20Telangana%20minister%20and%20KCR's%20son%20KT%20Rama%20Rao%20said%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bridiculous%26quot%3B%20that%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20was%20accusing%20KCR%20of%20promoting%20his%20family%20members%20within%20the%20party%20and%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697712540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F1lra3u8_ktr-kavitha-split_625x300_19_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-priyanka-gandhi-vadra-k-kavitha-ktr-on-gandhi-siblings-dynasty-charge-a-reply-from-kcrs-son-and-daughter-4496157%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hitting%20out%20at%20the%20Gandhi%20siblings%20over%20their%20dynasty%20charge%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20Telangana%20polls%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20K%20Chandrashekar's%20minister%20son%20and%20MLC%20daughter%20have%20said%20it%20is%20funny%20when%20great-grandchildren%20of%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20talk%20of%20family%20politics%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-priyanka-gandhi-vadra-k-kavitha-ktr-on-gandhi-siblings-dynasty-charge-a-reply-from-kcrs-son-and-daughter-4496157%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%