2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elgar%20Parishad%20Case%3A%20Since%20Evidence%20Tampering%20Not%20Ruled%20Out%2C%20Accused%20Want%20Chargesheets%20Quashed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19113842%2FThe-Wire-42.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Shoma%20Sen%20and%20Rona%20Wilson%2C%20named%20as%20accused%20in%20the%20Elgar%20Parishad%20case%2C%20have%20alleged%20in%20their%20petition%20before%20the%20Bombay%20high%20court%20that%20the%20prosecution%20violated%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%2C%201973%2C%20Indian%20Evidence%20Act%2C%201872%20and%20Information%20Technology%20Act%2C%202000%20in%20searching%20and%20seizing%20allegedly%20incriminating%20electronic%20documents%20from%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20urged%20the%20division%20Bench%20of%20Justice%20A.S.%20Gadkari%20and%20Justice%20Sharmila%20U.%20Deshmukh%20on%20Monday%2C%20October%2017%2C%20to%20quash%20the%20chargesheets%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAppearing%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20petitioners%2C%20senior%20advocate%20Anand%20Grover%20said%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA)%20is%20relying%20on%2010%20documents%20that%20were%20recovered%20allegedly%20from%20the%20electronic%20devices%20of%20Sen%20and%20Wilson.%20He%20told%20the%20court%20that%20the%20electronic%20documents%20are%20not%20attachments%20and%20are%20unsigned%2C%20lacking%20probative%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20the%20electronic%20documents%20were%20neither%20written%20nor%20transmitted%20by%20Sen%20or%20Wilson%20and%20classified%20them%20as%20%E2%80%9Cdigital%20hearsay%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheleaflet.in%2Fbombay-high-court-hears-petition-seeking-quashing-of-chargesheets-against-shoma-sen-and-rona-wilson%2F%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Leaflet%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGrover%20brought%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20the%20court%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F641904%2F%5C%22%3ESection%C2%A088A%20of%20the%20Indian%20Evidence%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%20prohibits%20the%20presumption%20of%20the%20originator%20of%20electronic%20evidence.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Pune%20Police%20had%20failed%20to%20record%20the%20hash%20value%20of%20the%20devices%20at%20the%20time%20of%20their%20seizure.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20hash%20value%20is%20a%20method%20widely%20known%20for%20the%20authentication%20of%20an%20electronic%20record%2C%20and%20police%20need%20to%20calculate%20the%20hash%20value%20when%20seizing%20electronic%20devices%20for%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20buttress%20his%20argument%2C%20Grover%20referred%20to%20Section%203%20of%20Information%20Technology%20(Security%20Procedure)%20Rules%2C%202004%2C%20which%20states%20that%20%E2%80%9Can%20electronic%20record%20shall%20be%C2%A0deemed%20to%20be%20a%20secure%20electronic%20record%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20the%20Act%20if%20it%20has%20been%20authenticated%20by%20means%20of%20a%20secure%20digital%20signature%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20the%20tampering%20of%20the%20documents%20cannot%20be%20ruled%20out%20given%20that%20Pune%20Police%20had%20sent%20the%20electronic%20device%20to%20the%20Forensic%20Science%20Laboratory%20(FSL)%20in%20Pune%20to%20ascertain%20its%20hash%20value.%20The%20mere%20sealing%20of%20electronic%20records%20at%20the%20place%20of%20seizure%20does%20not%20imply%20the%20security%20of%20data%20as%20per%20the%20law%2C%20Grover%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20Section%2014%20of%20the%20IT%20Act%2C%20the%20lawyer%20said%20the%20authenticity%20and%20integrity%20of%20electronic%20records%20that%20are%20not%20secure%20cannot%20presumed.%20To%20further%20his%20argument%2C%20he%20pointed%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20verdict%20in%202014%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22external%20noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F187283766%2F%5C%22%20data-wpel-link%3D%5C%22external%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EAnvar%20P.V.%20versus%20P.K.%20Basheer%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3Ecase%20and%20added%20that%20given%20electronic%20evidence%20is%20%E2%80%9Cvolatile%20in%20nature%E2%80%9D%2C%20it%20can%20be%20tampered%20with%20easily%20without%20any%20signs%20or%20indications.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20brought%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20the%20court%20that%20FSL%2C%20Pune%2C%20had%20failed%20to%20answer%20in%20its%20report%20whether%20the%20electronic%20device%20seized%20from%20Wilson%20had%20been%20tampered%20with.%20The%20clone%20copies%20of%20the%20seized%20devices%20%E2%80%93%20as%20required%20under%20Section%20207%20of%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%20%E2%80%93%20have%20not%20been%20provided%20to%20the%20accused%2C%20Grover%20informed%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20multiple%20requests%20to%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA)%20by%20the%20accused%20from%20June%202018%2C%20they%20have%20not%20been%20provided%20the%20cloned%20copies%2C%20and%20the%20matter%20is%20still%20pending%20before%20a%20special%20NIA%20court%2C%20Grover%20told%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20arguments%20of%20Grover%2C%20on%20behalf%20of%20Sen%20and%20Wilson%2C%20assume%20significance%20as%20there%20are%20allegations%20of%20severe%20malpractice%20by%20investigating%20authorities%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.medianama.com%2F2023%2F10%2F223-anand-grover-bhima-koregaon-seized-devices-security%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EMedianama%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Arsenal%20Consulting%20in%202021%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Frona-wilson-pegasus-iphone-arsenal%5C%22%3Eclaimed%3C%2Fa%3E%20traces%20of%20the%20NSO%20Group%E2%80%99s%20Pegasus%20spyware%20were%20found%20on%20Wilson%E2%80%99s%20phone%2C%20and%20also%20said%20he%20had%20received%20phishing%20emails%20from%20a%20%E2%80%9Cthreat%20actor%E2%80%9D%20between%202013%20and%202014%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fsecurity-researchers-claim-link-between-pune-police-and-hacking-campaign-against-bhima-koreagon-accused%5C%22%3ESentinelOne%3C%2Fa%3E%20alleged%20that%20hacking%20groups%20were%20used%20to%20target%20Wilson%E2%80%99s%20electronic%20devices.%20Even%20Amnesty%20International%20said%20last%20year%20that%20it%20had%20found%20evidence%20to%20show%20that%20Pune%20Police%20had%20hacked%20the%20emails%20of%20various%20arrested%20activists%2C%20including%20Wilson.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697711445000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19113842%2FThe-Wire-42.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Felgar-parishad-case-since-evidence-tampering-not-ruled-out-accused-want-chargesheets-quashed%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shoma%20Sen%20and%20Rona%20Wilson%20petitioned%20the%20Bombay%20high%20court%20alleging%20that%20norms%20were%20violated%20in%20searching%20and%20seizing%20electronic%20documents%20from%20them.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Felgar-parishad-case-since-evidence-tampering-not-ruled-out-accused-want-chargesheets-quashed%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Welspun%20bags%20contract%20to%20supply%2061%2C000%20MT%20of%20LSAW%20pipes%2C%20bends%20in%20Mideast%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697711413000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2016-11%2F15%2Ffull%2F1479205651-7683.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fwelspun-bags-contract-to-supply-61-000-mt-of-lsaw-pipes-bends-in-mideast-123101900537_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Welspun%20Corp%20Ltd%20(WCL)%20is%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20manufacturers%20of%20large-diameter%20pipes%20globally%22%2C%22a