t%3BI%20told%20her%20that%20I%20want%20to%20give%20up%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20post%20but%20this%20post%20is%20not%20letting%20me%20go%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gehlot%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20remarks%2C%20apparently%20made%20in%20a%20lighter%20note%2C%20are%20significant%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20tussle%20within%20Rajasthan%20Congress%20between%20the%20camps%20led%20by%20Mr%20Gehlot%20and%20Mr%20Pilot%2C%20his%20former%20deputy.%20A%20mutiny%20led%20by%20Mr%20Pilot%20had%20almost%20brought%20down%20the%20Congress%20government%20in%202020%20before%20the%20high%20command%20managed%20to%20save%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDoubling%20down%20on%20his%20dig%20at%20Mr%20Pilot%2C%20he%20said%20there%20must%20be%20something%20in%20him%20because%20of%20which%20the%20party%20high%20command%20had%20chosen%20him%20thrice%20to%20lead%20the%20state.%20He%2C%20however%2C%20added%20that%20any%20decision%20taken%20by%20the%20high%20command%20would%20be%20acceptable%20to%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20crucial%20November%2025%20election%2C%20both%20camps%20have%20tried%20to%20put%20up%20a%20united%20front%2C%20but%20barbs%20fly%20across%20from%20time%20to%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20a%20question%20on%20the%20delay%20in%20the%20Congress%20putting%20out%20its%20list%20of%20candidates%2C%20he%20said%20only%20the%20Opposition%20BJP%20was%20fretting%20over%20it.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20upset%20because%20we%20are%20not%20fighting.%20All%20the%20decisions%20are%20being%20taken%20after%20considering%20everyone's%20opinions.%20I%20am%20talking%20to%20Sachin%20Pilot's%20supporters%20too%2C%20deciding%20in%20their%20favour.%20Decisions%20are%20being%20taken%20smoothly.%20That's%20why%20only%20the%20BJP%20is%20not%20happy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20whether%20the%20party%20may%20deny%20tickets%20to%20its%20sitting%20legislators%2C%20he%20said%20the%20party%20will%20definitely%20change%20candidates%20if%20it%2