step-forward-towards-ushering-pilot-program-of-stamping-h-1b-visas-domestically%2Farticleshow%2F104553048.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UK%20Woman%20Wrongly%20Diagnosed%20With%20Cancer%20For%20Two%20Years%2C%20Wins%20Compensation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20resident%20of%20Yorkshire%2C%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20received%20compensation%20after%20being%20wrongly%20diagnosed%20with%20cancer%20and%20undergoing%20two%20years%20of%20unnecessary%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Megan%20Royle%2C%20a%2033-year-old%20from%20East%20Yorkshire%2C%20received%20a%20diagnosis%20of%20skin%20cancer.%20As%20a%20part%20of%20her%20treatment%2C%20she%20underwent%20immunotherapy%20and%20took%20measures%20to%20preserve%20her%20eggs%20because%20of%20the%20potential%20impact%20on%20her%20fertility.%20She%20is%20currently%20in%20a%20state%20of%20utter%20disbelief%20upon%20discovering%20that%20she%20was%20incorrectly%20diagnosed%20with%20cancer%20and%20underwent%20surgery%2C%20despite%20never%20actually%20having%20the%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-england-humber-67148523%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20BBC%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20was%20given%20the%20all-clear%20in%202021%3B%20a%20review%20showed%20she%20never%20had%20cancer%2C%20and%20she%20has%20now%20won%20compensation%20from%20the%20two%20NHS%20trusts%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMs.%20Royle%20from%20Beverley%20told%20the%20news%20outlet%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20just%20can't%20really%20believe%20something%20like%20this%20can%20happen%2C%20and%20still%20to%20this%20day%20I've%20not%20had%20an%20explanation%20as%20to%20how%20and%20why%20it%20happened.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20spent%20two%20years%20believing%20I%20had%20cancer%2C%20went%20through%20all%20the%20treatment%2C%20and%20then%20was%20told%20there%20had%20been%20no%20cancer%20at%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMs%20Royle%2C%20a%20theatrical%20make-up%20artist%20living%20in%20London%2C%20said%20that%20the%20news%20%26quot%3Btook%20a%20while%20to%20sink%20in.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou'd%20think%20the%20immediate%20emotion%20would%20be%20relief%2C%20and%2C%20in%20some%20sense%2C%20it%20was%2C%20but%20I'd%20say%20the%20greater%20emotions%20were%20frustration%20and%20anger.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20wasn't%20in%20a%20good%20place%20for%20quite%20some%20time%2C%20to%20be%20honest%2C%20strange%20as%20that%20may%20seem.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20outlet%20further%20reported%20that%20with%20Hull-based%20Hudgell%20Solicitors%2C%20Ms%20Royle%20has%20won%20an%20out-of-court%20settlement%20from%20the%20two%20London%20NHS%20trusts%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20news%20outlet%2C%20Ms%20Royle%2C%20represented%20by%20Hudgell%20Solicitors%20based%20in%20Hull%2C%20has%20successfully%20secured%20an%20out-of-court%20settlement%20from%20the%20two%20London%20NHS%20trusts%20responsible%20for%20her%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20from%20The%20Royal%20Marsden%20NHS%20Foundation%20Trust%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20wish%20to%20offer%20our%20sincere%20apologies%20to%20Megan%20Royle%20for%20the%20distress%20caused%20by%20her%20experience%20at%20our%20trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20pleased%20a%20settlement%20has%20been%20agreed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697710140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F4ov3uemg_megan-royle-from-east-yorkshire-was-diagnosed-with-skin-cancer-in-2019_625x300_19_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fuk-woman-wrongly-diagnosed-with-cancer-for-two-years-wins-compensation-4495910%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Megan%20was%20told%20she%20had%20been%20wrongly%20diagnosed%20with%20cancer%20after%20undergoing%20almost%20two%20years%20of%20treatment%20and%20egg%20preservation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%