com%2F2023%2Ftheater%2Fglobal%2Fmerchant-of-venice-uk-security-hamas-attacks-tracy-ann-oberman-1235761713%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ftheater%2Fglobal%2Fmerchant-of-venice-uk-security-hamas-attacks-tracy-ann-oberman-1235761713%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel%E2%80%99s%20War%20on%20Palestinians%3A%20Language%20in%20the%20Service%20of%20the%20Unspeakable%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19092706%2FF8t8SUEWMAAvoa0.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ELet%20us%20start%20with%20acceptance%20of%20a%20fundamental%20moral-political%20reality.%20The%20relationship%20between%20the%20Palestinians%20in%20the%20occupied%20territories%20and%20Israel%20is%20that%20of%20the%20oppressed%20vis-%C3%A0-vis%20the%20oppressor.%20Through%20the%20use%20of%20the%20most%20brutal%20forms%20of%20violence%2C%20both%20overt%20and%20covert%2C%20Israel%20has%20maintained%20the%20longest%20running%20illegal%20occupation%20of%20the%2020th%20and%2021st%20centuries.%20Another%20moral-political%20principle%20follows%20from%20this.%20While%20the%20side%20that%20is%20oppressed%20has%20the%20right%2C%20under%20international%20law%2C%20to%20use%20military%20and%20other%20means%20to%20resist%20and%20fight%20against%20the%20Occupying%20State%20(of%20course%2C%20in%20conformity%20with%20international%20humanitarian%20law)%2C%20the%20Occupier%20has%20%3Cem%3Eno%20right%20whatsoever%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20use%20military%20or%20any%20other%20mean%20to%20sustain%2C%20let%20alone%20deepen%2C%20that%20structure%20of%20injustice.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%20let%20us%20look%20at%20the%20assault%20carried%20out%20by%20Hamas%20through%20the%20prism%20of%20what%20Malcolm%20X%20said%20when%20he%20declared%20that%20the%20struggle%20for%20black%20liberation%20will%20use%20%E2%80%9Cany%20means%20necessary%E2%80%9D.%20Why%20did%20he%20say%20this%20and%20was%20he%20justified%20in%20making%20such%20a%20blanket%20call%3F%20The%20wisdom%20in%20what%20he%20said%20was%20his%20recognition%20that%20the%20oppressor%20will%20use%20any%20means%20necessary%20to%20maintain%20its%20domination%20so%20why%20should%20the%20victims%20forego%20what%20their%20opponent%20will%20undoubtedly%20do%20time%20and%20again%3F%20As%20a%20characterisation%20of%20the%20various%20means%20that%20Israel%20has%20been%20using%20all%20these%20decades%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20use%20after%20the%20Hamas%20assault%2C%20Malcolm%20X%E2%80%99s%20warning%20is%20both%20prescient%20and%20accurate.%20But%20this%20does%20not%20mean%20the%20side%20that%20is%20oppressed%20should%20follow%20this%20dictum%2C%C2%A0%20especially%20when%20it%20knows%20the%20oppressor%20will%20continue%20to%20do%20so.%20Going%20after%20a%20military%20base%20and%20attacking%20enemy%20soldiers%20is%20justified%20but%20never%20an%20assault%20on%20innocent%20unarmed%20civilians.%20In%20spite%20of%20the%20absence%20of%20any%20universally%20accepted%20definition%20of%20terrorism%2C%20there%20is%20enough%20of%20a%20global%20consensus%20to%20recognise%20this%20as%20a%20terrorist%20act%20that%20must%20be%20condemned%20no%20matter%20which%20side%20does%20it.%20But%20then%20how%20is%20it%20that%20Israel%20is%20able%20to%20get%20away%2C%20both%20before%20and%20after%20the%20Hamas%20assault%2C%20with%20its%20assaults%20on%20civilians%20not%20being%20widely%20recognised%20at%20home%20and%20abroad%20as%20terrorism%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EWatch%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Watch%20%7C%20'Israel%E2%80%99s%20Fragility%20Is%2010%2F10%3B%20Biden%E2%80%99s%20Visit%20Offers%20Netanyahu%20Excuse%20to%20Avoid%20Tough%20Action'%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-israels-fragility-is-10-10-bidens-visit-offers-netanyahu-excuse-to-avoid-tough-action%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Israel%E2%80%99s%20Fragility%20Is%2010%2F10%3B%20Biden%E2%80%99s%20Visit%20Offers%20Netanyahu%20Excuse%20to%20Avoid%20Tough%20Action%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20where%20the%20power%20of%20language%20and%20the%20arsenal%20of%20words%20used%20and%20not%20used%2C%20by%20Israel%20and%20its%20supporters%2C%20comes%20in.%20The%20current%20Israeli%20defence%20minister%2C%20Yoav%20Gallant%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fprogram%2Fnewsfeed%2F2023%2F10%2F9%2Fisraeli-defence-minister-orders-complete-siege-on-gaza%5C%22%3Ehas%20called%20Gazans%20%E2%80%9Chuman%20animals%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20even%20as%20the%20ongoing%20devastation%20of%20Gaza%20and%20its%20public%20is%20being%20carried%20out.%20This%20mental%20de-humanisation%20is%20not%20an%20emotional%20%E2%80%98overreaction%E2%80%99%20to%20what%20has%20recently%20happened%20in%20Israel%20but%20reveals%20the%20basic%20but%20necessary%20mindset%20of%20so%20many%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20top%20leaders.%20It%20is%20necessary%20because%20it%20is%20the%20only%20way%20for%20them%20to%20rationalise%20and%20justify%20both%20to%20themselves%20and%20to%20the%20public%20their%20longstanding%20involvement%20in%20the%20brutal%20incarceration%20and%20mass%20killings%20of%20Palestinians.%20During%20an%20earlier%202012%20Gaza%20bombardment%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Freliefweb.int%2Freport%2Foccupied-palestinian-territory%2F%25E2%2580%2598flattening%25E2%2580%2599-gaza%5C%22%3Edeputy%20prime%20minister%20Eli%20Yishai%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20must%20blow%20Gaza%20back%20to%20the%20Middle%20Ages%2C%20destroying%20all%20the%20infrastructure%20including%20roads%20and%20water.%E2%80%9D%20Moshe%20Feiglin%2C%20deputy%20speaker%20of%20the%20Knesset%2C%20laid%20out%20a%20seven-step%20plan%20for%20the%20destruction%20of%20all%20infrastructure%20and%20issued%20a%20single%20ultimatum%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthehill.com%2Fblogs%2Fcongress-blog%2Fforeign-policy%2F214080-israeli-extremist%2F%5C%22%3Eto%20the%20enemy%20population%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20defined%20as%20any%20who%20did%20not%20move%20from%20Gaza%20to%20Sinai.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20call%20for%20such%20an%20evacuation%20out%20of%20Gaza%20to%20Egypt%20has%20been%20repeated%20now%20by%20the%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20government%20which%20gave%20civilians%20north%20of%20Wadi%20Gaza%2024%20hours%20to%20leave%20and%20go%20south.%20In%20July-August%202014%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmerip.org%2F2015%2F10%2Foperation-protective-edge%2F%5C%22%3Emassive%2051-day%20assault%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20codenamed%20%E2%80%98Operation%20Protective%20Edge%E2%80%99%20(one%20of%20a%20number%20of%20such%20brutal%20campaigns%20against%20Gaza)%2C%20resulted%20in%20over%202%2C200%20dead%20and%20over%205000%20injured.%20Shortly%20before%20this%2C%20the%20Knesset%20member%20Ayelet%20Shaked%2C%20later%20to%20serve%20as%20justice%20minister%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thedailybeast.com%2Fisraeli-politician-declares-war-on-the-palestinian-people%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eposted%20inflammatory%20remarks%20by%20a%20Netanyahu%20associate%20on%20Facebook%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Palestinian%20people%20have%20declared%20war%20on%20us%2C%20and%20we%20must%20respond%20with%20war%E2%80%A6%20Who%20is%20the%20enemy%3F%20The%20Palestinian%20people%E2%80%A6in%20wars%20the%20enemy%20is%20usually%20an%20entire%20people%2C%20including%20its%20elderly%20and%20its%20women%2C%20its%20cities%20and%20its%20villages%2C%20its%20property%20and%20its%20infrastructure.%E2%80%9D%20Women%20who%20give%20birth%20to%20%E2%80%9Cmartyrs%E2%80%9D%20should%20follow%20their%20sons%20(i.e.%2C%20into%20their%20graves).%20%E2%80%9COtherwise%2C%20more%20little%20snakes%20will%20be%20raised%20there.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20extraordinary%20that%20Israel%2C%20the%20occupier%2C%20then%20and%20now%2C%20calls%20for%20a%20%E2%80%98war%E2%80%99%20against%20the%20occupied!%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWords%20used%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20public%20discourse%20around%20terrorism%20when%20used%20by%20governments%20and%20their%20media%20drum-beaters%20is%20selective%2C%20hypocritical%20and%20morally%20dishonest.%20Terrorism%20must%20not%20be%20seen%20as%20primarily%20a%20reference%20to%20a%20category%20of%20persons%20but%20as%20referring%20to%20a%20means%2C%20a%20tactic%2C%20a%20technique%2C%20a%20method.%20This%20is%20precisely%20why%20there%20are%20three%20kinds%20of%20agents%20that%20carry%20out%20terrorist%20acts%20and%20campaigns%20%E2%80%93%20the%20individual%2C%20the%20non-state%20group%20and%20the%20apparatuses%20of%20the%20state.%20The%20scale%20of%20victims%20and%20of%20general%20devastation%20caused%20by%20state%20violence%20massively%20dwarfs%20that%20caused%20by%20a%20non-state%20group%20actor.%20This%20is%20obviously%20because%20it%20has%20much%20greater%20capacity%20to%20exercise%20violence%20and%20does%20so.%20But%20the%20%E2%80%98grand%E2%80%99%20character%20of%20its%20terrorist%20actions%20are%20much%20more%20easily%20disguised%20because%20they%20are%20rationalised%20in%20the%20name%20of%20grandiose%20ends%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%98national%20security%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98unity%20and%20integrity%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20nation%2C%20%E2%80%98protecting%20democracy%E2%80%99%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20fundamental%20nature%20of%20any%20political%20actor%2C%20good%20or%20bad%2C%20is%20not%20defined%20by%20its%20means%20but%20by%20its%20programme%2C%20its%20ideology%2C%20its%20goals.%20But%20once%20the%20term%20%E2%80%98terrorist%E2%80%99%20is%20taken%20to%20define%20the%20political%20nature%20of%20the%20non-state%20actor%2C%20it%20is%20taken%20as%20justification%20for%20identifying%20all%20its%20members%20or%20even%20the%20civilians%20they%20claim%20to%20represent%20as%20terrorists%20and%20targets%20%E2%80%93%20and%20to%20seek%20their%20physical%20elimination%20irrespective%20of%20whether%20they%20have%20carried%20out%20a%20terrorist%20act%20or%20whether%20their%20culpability%20has%20been%20established.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22What%20India%20Is%20Getting%20Wrong%20About%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20Conflict%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fwhat-india-is-getting-wrong-about-the-israel-hamas-conflict%5C%22%3EWhat%20India%20Is%20Getting%20Wrong%20About%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20Conflict%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20how%20are%20the%20terrorist%20actions%20by%20the%20state%20to%20be%20justified%3F%20Simply%20call%20its%20unspeakable%20actions%20that%20violate%20basic%20humanitarian%20principles%2C%20rights%20and%20laws%20%E2%80%98counter-terrorism%E2%80%99.%20Other%20words%20and%20phrases%20can%20now%20be%20used%20to%20further%20cover%20up%20their%20culpabilities%20as%20is%2C%20for%20example%2C%20widely%20being%20done%20in%20the%20mainstream%20India%20media%20for%20Israel.%20So%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20murderous%20actions%20in%20Gaza%20(and%20in%20the%20West%20Bank)%20should%20be%20described%20as%20%E2%80%98retaliation%E2%80%99%2C%20as%20%E2%80%98reprisals%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInsofar%20as%20there%20are%20those%20who%20describe%20Hamas%20as%20motivated%20not%20so%20much%20by%20the%20desire%20to%20liberate%20Palestinians%20but%20by%20an%20ideologically%20driven%20%3Cem%3Ejihadi%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98terroristic%E2%80%99%20fervour%2C%20how%20many%20among%20them%20or%20others%20would%20be%20prepared%20to%20declare%20that%20the%20Israeli%20state%E2%80%99s%20behaviour%20is%20motivated%20by%20a%20%3Cem%3EZionist%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%98terroristic%E2%80%99%20fervour!%20Islam%20or%20Judaism%2C%20like%20any%20religion%2C%20can%20be%20selectively%20interpreted%20to%20justify%20politically%20racist%20and%20exclusivist%20purposes%20but%20no%20religion%20is%20inherently%20so.%20Zionism%20is%20not%20a%20religion%20but%20a%20political%20ideology%20which%20is%20inherently%20exclusivist.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20little%20more%20difficult%20for%20Israel%20in%20its%20pursuit%20of%20Hamas%20to%20get%20away%20with%20justifying%20the%20%E2%80%98collective%20punishment%E2%80%99%20of%20Gazans.%20Here%20the%20language%20used%20to%20pre-empt%20any%20criticism%20and%20condemnation%20of%20its%20terrorist%20killings%20of%20civilians%2C%20is%20the%20accusation%20that%20Hamas%20is%20%E2%80%98hiding%20behind%20civilians%E2%80%99.%20Like%20all%20colonised%20people%2C%20those%20willing%20to%20carry%20out%20armed%20struggle%20against%20the%20colonial%20oppressor%20must%20do%20so%20in%20an%20underground%20fashion.%20Moreover%2C%20there%20is%20no%20possibility%20of%20there%20being%20a%20geographically%20%E2%80%99remote%E2%80%99%20area%20separated%20from%20the%20mass%20of%20civilians%20in%20what%20is%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20densely%20populated%20zone.%20Israel%20knows%20this%20and%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20care.%20The%20definition%20of%20terrorist%20behaviour%20applies%20universally.%20There%20are%20never%20any%20excuses%20for%20intentionally%20or%20knowingly%20or%20indiscriminately%20killing%20civilians.%20Israel%20has%20no%20right%20to%20attack%20Gaza%20with%20or%20without%20evacuation%20warnings%20which%2C%20when%20occasionally%20given%2C%20are%20for%20the%20purposes%20of%20pretending%20to%20the%20global%20public%20that%20it%20will%20be%20justified%20in%20carrying%20out%20its%20subsequent%20brutalities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25125403%2FNetanyahu.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25125403%2FNetanyahu.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25125403%2FNetanyahu-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25125403%2FNetanyahu-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-664935%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBenjamin%20Netanyahu.%20Photo%3A%20Av%20Jolanda%20Flubacher%2FWORLD%20ECONOMIC%20FORUM%2Fswiss-image.ch.%20CC%20BY-SA%202.0.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EDeclaring%20a%20%E2%80%98war%20on%20terrorism%E2%80%99%2C%20as%20Israel%20has%20also%20done%2C%20is%20fraudulent.%20How%20can%20one%20declare%20a%20war%20against%20a%20method!%20But%20deceitfully%20using%20the%20term%20%E2%80%98war%E2%80%99%20dramatically%20expands%20the%20range%20of%20activity%20that%20can%20be%20undertaken%20by%20Israel.%20To%20win%20a%20war%2C%20one%20can%20take%20all%20manner%20of%20pre-emptive%20and%20pro-active%20large-scale%20military%20actions%20in%20the%20name%20of%20%E2%80%98self-defence%E2%80%99%20against%20the%20%E2%80%98enemy%E2%80%99.%20Most%20importantly%2C%20the%20home%20territory%20of%20the%20presumed%20foe%20can%20then%20be%20transformed%20into%20a%20supposedly%20legitimate%20theatre%20of%20war.%20This%20is%20how%20Israel%20and%20its%20supporters%20try%20to%20construct%20their%20discourse%20of%20justification.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWords%20not%20used%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20three%20terms%20that%20are%20of%20the%20utmost%20truth%20that%20Israel%20will%20not%20use.%20First%2C%20the%20proper%20description%20of%20Israel%20is%20that%20it%20is%20a%20%E2%80%98settler-colonial%E2%80%99%20state%2C%20indeed%20now%20the%20only%20one%20in%20the%20world.%20Second%2C%20it%20is%20also%20an%20apartheid%20state%20fitting%20the%202002%20Rome%20Statute%20definition%20of%20a%20state%20whose%20%E2%80%98crimes%20against%20humanity%E2%80%99%20are%20%E2%80%9Ccommitted%20in%20the%20context%20of%20an%20institutionalised%20regime%20of%20systematic%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FOppression%5C%22%3Eoppression%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FDominance_hierarchy%5C%22%3Edomination%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0by%20one%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FRace_(classification_of_human_beings)%5C%22%3Eracial%20group%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20any%20other%20racial%20group%20or%20groups%20and%20committed%20with%20the%20intention%20of%20maintaining%20that%20regime%E2%80%9D.%20Third%2C%20similar%20to%20the%20South%20African%20apartheid%20regime%2C%20here%20too%20there%20is%20the%20deliberate%20%E2%80%99Bantustanisation%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20West%20Bank%20so%20as%20to%20maximise%20Israeli%E2%80%99s%20military%20control%20over%20the%20Palestinians%20there%20and%20over%20its%20resources%2C%20especially%20water%2C%20while%C2%A0%20its%20illegal%20Jewish%20settlements%20will%20continue%20to%20expand.%20But%20even%20worse%20than%20this%2C%20has%20been%20the%20situation%20and%20treatment%20of%20Gazans%20which%20had%20no%20parallel%20under%20the%20South%20African%20apartheid%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20now%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20two-state%20solution%20has%20long%20been%20dead.%20Israel%20was%20never%20serious%20about%20it%2C%20as%20any%20honest%20investigation%20of%20its%20behaviour%20in%20the%20years%20immediately%20after%20the%201993%20Oslo%20Accords%20will%20make%20clear.%20What%20talk%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98need%20to%20pursue%20the%20two-state%20solution%E2%80%99%20does%20is%20to%20enable%20other%20governments%2C%20most%20certainly%20including%20India%2C%20to%20continue%20paying%20diplomatic%20lip%20service%20to%20the%20Palestinian%20cause%20while%20pursuing%20deeper%20relations%20with%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22By%20Siding%20With%20Israel%2C%20India%20Is%20Jettisoning%20Decades%20of%20Middle%20East%20Statesmanship%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fby-siding-with-israel-india-is-jettisoning-decades-of-middle-east-statesmanship%5C%22%3EBy%20Siding%20With%20Israel%2C%20India%20Is%20Jettisoning%20Decades%20of%20Middle%20East%20Statesmanship%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20where%20does%20the%20Palestinian%20struggle%20for%20justice%20go%3F%20It%20must%20be%20to%20fight%20for%20the%20end%20of%20apartheid%20and%20therefore%20for%20full%20rights%20and%20equality%20with%20Jews%20in%20a%20genuinely%20democratic%20non-Zionist%2C%20multi-ethnic%2C%20multi-racial%20society.%20The%20tragedy%20of%20the%20Palestinians%20is%20that%20for%20too%20long%20a%20remarkable%20and%20courageous%20people%20have%20not%20had%20the%20kind%20of%20leadership%20they%20deserve.%20More%20and%20more%20Palestinians%20today%20are%20coming%20around%20to%20this%20perspective%2C%20one%20that%20if%20officially%20adopted%20by%20a%20newer%20leadership%2C%20would%20have%20much%20greater%20democratic%20appeal%20worldwide.%20This%20would%20greatly%20worry%20the%20Israeli%20government%20and%20the%20US%20seeking%20to%20construct%20a%20wider%20regional%20alliance%20structure%20with%20the%20neighbouring%20Middle%20East%20dictatorships.%20The%20Palestinian%20cause%20would%20link%20much%20more%20strongly%20to%20the%20popular%20aspirations%20in%20the%20Arab%20world%20to%20rid%20themselves%20of%20their%20own%20dictatorships.%20Here%2C%20the%202011%20mass%20uprisings%2C%20though%20currently%20contained%2C%20have%20rung%20the%20warning%20bell%20for%20what%20can%20and%20will%20happen%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20one%20important%20source%20of%20hope%20for%20the%20Palestinian%20cause.%20The%20other%20is%20that%20Israel%20cannot%20completely%20or%20forever%20crush%20the%20Palestinian%20resistance.%20Their%20struggle%20for%20justice%20will%20continue.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fachin-vanaik%5C%22%3EAchin%20Vanaik%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20writer%20and%20social%20activist%2C%20a%20former%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Delhi%20and%20Delhi-based%20Fellow%20of%20the%20Transnational%20Institute%2C%20Amsterdam.%20He%20is%20the%20author%20of%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Painful%20Transition%3A%20Bourgeois%20Democracy%20in%20India%20and%20The%20Rise%20of%20Hindu%20Authoritarianism.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697707834000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19092706%2FF8t8SUEWMAAvoa0.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisraels-war-on-palestinians-language-in-the-service-of-the-unspeakable%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20is%20extraordinary%20that%20Israel%2C%20the%20occupier%2C%20calls%20for%20a%20%E2%80%98war%E2%80%99%20against%20the%20occupied.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisraels-war-on-palestinians-language-in-the-service-of-the-unspeakable%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%3A%20Jewish%20Activists%20Protest%20in%20Solidarity%20with%20Palestine%2C%20Demand%20Ceasefire%20in%20Gaza%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19122228%2Fimage-1405.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Hundreds%20of%20Jewish%20activists%20demonstrated%20on%20Capitol%20Hill%20and%20protested%20inside%20a%20House%20office%20building%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20October%2018%2C%20demanding%20that%20the%20Biden%20administration%20and%20lawmakers%20push%20for%20a%20ceasefire%20in%20Gaza%2C%20as%20Israeli%20airstrikes%20continue%20and%20the%20humanitarian%20crisis%20intensifies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUS%20Capitol%20Police%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fabout-300-pleading-for-ceasefire-were-arrested-on-capitol-hill-organizers-say%2Farticleshow%2F104543267.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Earrested%3C%2Fa%3E%20around%20300%20people%20who%20were%20protesting%20inside%20the%20House%20office%20building%20and%20said%20three%20protesters%20were%20charged%20with%20assault%20on%20a%20police%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20rally%20was%20organised%20by%