estine-war-thank-you-meta-israel-after-mark-zuckerberg-calls-hamas-attacks-pure-evil-4483335%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BThank%20You%20Meta%26quot%3B%3A%20Israel%20After%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20Calls%20Hamas%20Attacks%20%26quot%3BPure%20Evil%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeta%20also%20said%20that%20any%20content%20%26quot%3Bcontaining%20praise%26quot%3B%20for%20Hamas%20will%20not%20be%20allowed%20on%20Facebook%20or%20Instagram%2C%20as%20the%20group%20falls%20under%20its%20Dangerous%20Organization%20designation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20policies%20are%20designed%20to%20keep%20people%20safe%20on%20our%20apps%20while%20giving%20everyone%20a%20voice%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabout.fb.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F10%2Fmetas-efforts-regarding-israel-hamas-war%2F%5C%22%3EMeta%20said%20in%20the%20update%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20apply%20these%20policies%20equally%20around%20the%20world%20and%20there%20is%20no%20truth%20to%20the%20suggestion%20that%20we%20are%20deliberately%20suppressing%20voice%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOther%20temporary%20changes%20implemented%20by%20Meta%20for%20content%20related%20to%20Israel-Hamas%20war%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EDefault%20setting%20for%20who%20can%20comment%20on%20newly%20created%20public%20Facebook%20posts%20of%20people%20in%20the%20region%20changed%20to%20Friends%20and%2For%20established%20followers%20only.%20Meta%20said%20users%20globally%20can%20choose%20to%20use%20this%20setting%20and%20opt%20in%20or%20out%20at%20any%20time.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EBulk%20deletion%20of%20comments%20made%20easier%20and%20display%20of%20first%20one%20or%20two%20comments%20under%20posts%20in%20Feed%20disabled%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EFacebook%20has%20also%20rolled%20out%20the%20'Lock%20Your%20Profile'%20tool%20in%20the%20region.%20These%20users%20can%20lock%20their%20profile%20in%20one%20step%2C%20enhancing%20profile%20privacy%20by%20restricting%20access%20to%20non-friends.%3C