ot%20contained%20swiftly%2C%20the%20fallout%20of%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict%20may%20inflict%20more%20catastrophic%20collateral%20damage%20on%20the%20global%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20fear%20that%20other%20countries%20could%20be%20drawn%20into%20this%20conflict.%20In%20particular%2C%20if%20Iran%2C%20Egypt%2C%20and%20Syria%20were%20to%20join%20this%20religious%20war%20%E2%80%93%20with%20the%20presumption%20that%20this%20war%20is%20affecting%20the%20sentiment%20of%20the%20Arab%20and%20Muslim%20world%20%E2%80%93%20the%C2%A0price%20of%20crude%20may%20spin%20out%20of%20control.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2023%2F10%2F13%2Foil-prices-crude-futures-rise-after-us-tightens-sanctions-on-russia.html%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2023%2F10%2F13%2Foil-prices-crude-futures-rise-after-us-tightens-sanctions-on-russia.html%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1697781640629000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw3I5iQvtlwVpNhfatk3tnj6%5C%22%3Eprice%20of%20crude%20oil%C2%A0has%20jumped%206%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20the%20start%20of%20this%20crisis.%20The%20oil%20price%20has%20inched%20towards%20%2490%20a%20barrel%2C%20and%20it%20could%20cross%20the%20symbolic%20danger%20mark%20of%20%24100%20per%20barrel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20that%20happens%2C%20interest%20rates%20will%20stay%20higher%20for%20longer%2C%20not%20only%20in%20the%20US%20but%20in%20India%20as%20well.%20There%E2%80%99s%20also%20the%20possibility%20of%20another%20financial%20accident%20in%20the%20US%2C%20like%20more%20banks%20going%20belly%20up.%20Furthermore%2C%20the%20dollar%20index%20inching%20up%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20bode%20well%20for%20India.%20If%20fickle%20FII%2FFPI%20money%20rushes%20out%2C%20the%20much-valorised%20domestic%20retail%20money%20may%20hold%20up%20the%20market%20only%20for%20some%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20to%20be%20noted%2C%20that%20for%20India%2C%20crude%20has%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%