1-12%2C%20%3Cem%3EBusinessline%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fextreme-poverty-in-india-eased-in-2021-but-remained-above-2018-level-123101801314_1.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20results%20for%202022-23%20and%202023-24%20CES%20are%20likely%20to%20come%20only%20after%20the%202024%20general%20elections%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fresults-of-consumer-expenditure-surveys-2022-23-2023-24-only-after-2024-elections-report%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20reported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20findings%20of%20a%20similar%20exercise%20done%20by%20the%20government%20in%202017-2018%20were%20withheld%20but%20the%20leaked%20data%20had%20shown%20a%20rise%20in%20poverty%20levels%20and%20a%2045-year%20high%20in%20unemployment%20in%202018.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Findia-poverty-estimates-shot-in-dark%5C%22%3ERecent%20Poverty%20Estimates%20Are%20Little%20More%20Than%20a%20Shot%20in%20the%20Dark%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFormer%20member%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20Planning%20Commission%20N.C.%20Saxena%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fextreme-poverty-in-india-eased-in-2021-but-remained-above-2018-level-123101801314_1.html%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20there%20were%20many%20reasons%20why%20poverty%20might%20have%20increased%20before%20the%20pandemic%20in%202018-19.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20government%E2%80%99s%20own%202017-18%20consumption%20survey%20that%20it%20junked%20had%20shown%20that%20poverty%20increased%20in%20India.%20In%20the%202005-2015%20period%2C%20there%20was%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20investment%20in%20construction%2C%20which%20declined%20after%202015.%20So%2C%20a%20large%20number%20of%20people%20who%20were%20involved%20i