t%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexclusive%20pieces%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20mosaic%20and%20wood%20art%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20come%20cheap.%20Also%2C%20since%20only%20the%20two%20of%20them%20handle%20the%20creative%20aspect%20of%20the%20business%2C%20they%20cannot%20make%20products%20in%20large%20numbers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20there%20are%20two%20other%20people%20in%20their%20workshop%20who%20help%20with%20the%20mosaic%20works%20along%20with%20three%20freelancing%20carpenters%20and%20polishers%20for%20the%20woodwork.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20wall%20arts%20from%20their%20studio%20start%20at%20Rs%202%2C000-2%2C500%20per%20square%20foot%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20intricacy%20of%20design.%20The%20price%20of%20a%20driftwood%20centre%20table%20ranges%20from%20Rs%2018%2C000%20to%20Rs%2040%2C000%20which%20depends%20on%20the%20size%20and%20the%20quality%20of%20wood.%20Mosaic%20garden%20tables%2C%20two%20feet%20in%20diameter%2C%20cost%20Rs%2012%2C500.%20Floor%20lamps%20are%20priced%20at%20Rs%207%2C000-10%2C000.%20Planters%20range%20from%20Rs%205%2C000-15%2C000%2C%20depending%20on%20size.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYohann%20has%20a%20residence-cum-studio%20in%20Bandra%20where%20clients%20can%20take%20a%20look%20at%20the%20products.%20The%20company%20gets%20orders%20from%20across%20India.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20fact%2C%20more%20than%20half%20of%20our%20clientele%20is%20outside%20Mumbai.%20Our%20products%20are%20large%20and%20meant%20for%20large%20spaces.%20Around%2060%20percent%20of%20our%20pieces%20are%20custom-made%20while%2040%20percent%20is%20from%20an%20inventory.%20We%20are%20now%20looking%20to%20grow%20the%20business%20through%20projects%20to%20do%20up%20villas%20and%20homes%20by%20collaborating%20with%20interior%20designers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20537px)%20100vw%2C%20537px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDri