ferent.%20It%20is%20the%20joy%20and%20immense%20satisfaction%20of%20creating%20art%20from%20waste%20that%20drives%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Naomi.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDriftwood%20has%20to%20undergo%20a%20rigorous%20process%20before%20it%20can%20be%20worked%20with.%20It%20involves%20scrubbing%20and%20cleaning%20the%20piece%2C%20bleaching%20it%20over%20a%20period%20of%20weeks%20to%20remove%20the%20insects%20as%20well%20as%20lighten%20the%20wood%C2%A0tones.%20Then%20it%20is%20protected%20from%20termites%20and%20kept%20out%20in%20the%20sun%20to%20dry%20thoroughly%2C%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20entire%20day%20is%20spent%20in%20my%20workshop%2C%20especially%20if%20we%20have%20hard%20deadlines.%20At%20times%2C%20day%20creeps%20into%20night.%20Sometimes%2C%20I%20even%20forget%20to%20eat.%20I%20hire%20more%20hands%20on%20a%20daily%20wage%20basis%20if%20I%20need%20extra%20assistance.%20While%20I%20lay%20the%20creative%20groundwork%20for%20a%20piece%2C%20the%20machine%20work%20is%20handled%20by%20my%20team%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20clients%20like%20The%20Dignity%20Foundation%20for%20the%20elderly%2C%20who%20got%20a%20piece%20made%20for%20their%20newest%20project%20in%20Neral%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20and%20the%20LV%20Prasad%20eye%20hospital%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20or%20the%20three%20murals%20they%20made%20for%20the%20Santori%20Resort%20at%20Mulshi%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20the%20studio%20keeps%20busy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20started%20my%20business%20in%20my%20fifties%2C%20much%20against%20everyone%E2%80%99s%20advice%20and%20with%20many%20negative%20comments%20from%20sceptics%20and%20naysayers.%20Some%20people%20felt%20I%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F215357%2Findia-philanthropy-david-rockefeller-shibulal-family-philanthropic-initiatives-changemakers-education%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etoo%20old%20to%20start%20a%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20something%20I%20was%20not%20experienced%20in.%20I%20am%20happy%20to%20say%20that%20I%20am%20still%20here%20and%20enjoying%20my%20work%20all%20while%20creating%20products%20that%20people%20truly%20appreciate%2C%E2%80%9D%20Naomi%20says%20with%20a%20smile.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FBook-shelf-1697535601.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20book%20shelf%20made%20with%20using%20a%20reclaimed%20piece%20of%20wood.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FBook-shelf-1697535601.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FBook-shelf-1697535601-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FBook-shelf-1697535601-500x667.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FBook-shelf-1697535601-768x1024.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FBook-shelf-1697535601-1152x1536.jpg%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FBook-shelf-1697535601-640x853.jpg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FBook-shelf-1697535601-150x200.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332392%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20book%20shelf%20made%20with%20using%20a%20reclaimed%20piece%20of%20wood.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EAll%20picture%20credits%20to%20The%20Druid%E2%80%99s%20Garden.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697552503000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FNature-themed-wall-art_11zon-1697535460.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D332361%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Naomi%20and%20Yohann%20Pereira's%20venture%2C%20The%20Druid%E2%80%99s%20Garden%2C%20makes%20unique%2C%20aesthetic%20and%20sustainable%20products%20by%20using%20reclaimed%20and%20upcycled%20raw%20materials.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Aruna%20Raghuram%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332361%2Fmumbai-artist-mom-son-use-driftwood-and-mosaic-tiles-to-make-art-furniture%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meet%20Hare%20Ram%20Pandey%2C%20The%2066-YO%20Who%20Dedicated%20His%20Life%20to%20Raising%2035%20Girls%20As%20His%20Daughters%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOn%209%20December%202004%2C%20Hare%20Ram%20Pandey%E2%80%99s%20life%20changed%20forever.%20He%20found%20a%20newborn%20girl%20abandoned%20in%20a%20forest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20found%20this%20girl%2C%20she%20was%20in%20a%20very%20bad%20condition.%20There%20were%20ants%20all%20over%20her%20umbilical%20cord%20and%20her%20back.%20I%20immediately%20took%20her%20to%20a%20hospital%2C%20where%20she%20was%20treated%20for%20almost%2021%20days.%20The%20doctor%20had%20also%20lost%20hope%20but%20I%20knew%20that%20this%20girl%20was%20God%E2%80%99s%20gift%20to%20me%20and%20would%20survive%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pandey.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20named%20the%20girl%20Taapsee%2C%20and%20today%20the%2019-year-old%20is%20one%20among%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330978%2Fkamlesh-atwal-started-nanakmatta-public-school-uttarakhand-holistic-education-for-students%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPandey%E2%80%99s%2035%20daughters%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETaking%20care%20of%20Taapsee%20gave%20this%2066-year-old%20a%20new%20sense%20of%20purpose%20in%20life%20and%20led%20to%20him%20becoming%20a%20saviour