er%20abandoned%20newborn%20girl.%20He%20rescued%20her%20and%20took%20her%20to%20the%20hospital.%20When%20this%20girl%2C%20named%20Khushi%2C%20survived%20as%20well%2C%20the%20social%20worker%20resolved%20to%20make%20an%20ashram%20for%20such%20abandoned%20girls.%20He%20registered%20his%20Narayan%20Sewa%20Ashram%20as%20a%20trust.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20first%20saw%20Taapsee%2C%20my%20soul%20bonded%20with%20this%20tiny%20human.%20How%20could%20anyone%20abandon%20these%20girls%3F%20They%20deserve%20to%20live%20and%20I%20resolved%20to%20help%20as%20many%20girls%20as%20I%20could%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20the%20local%20and%20railway%20police%2C%20along%20with%20the%20local%20administration%20in%20Deoghar%2C%20would%20call%20Pandey%20whenever%20they%20found%20an%20abandoned%20girl.%20Called%20%3Cem%3EBaba%3C%2Fem%3E%20(dad)%20by%20these%20young%20girls%2C%20Pandey%20and%20his%20wife%20would%20lovingly%20welcome%20another%20such%20%E2%80%98daughter%E2%80%99%20into%20their%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20in%20an%20%3Cem%3Eadivasi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(tribal)%20area.%20There%20is%20no%20trust%20like%20ours%20in%20a%20150-200-km%20radius.%20So%20all%20the%20calls%20across%20this%20area%20are%20directed%20to%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20raise%2C%20nurture%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F328239%2Fanimal-rescue-and-rehabilitation-centres-in-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeducate%20these%20girls%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20their%20own%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20locals.%20Taapsee%20and%20Khushi%20are%20in%20junior%20college%20now%20and%20aspire%20to%20be%20doctors.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20Pandey%20is%20working%20towards%20a%20noble%20cause%2C%20the%20going%20has%20been%20tough%20for%20the%20sexagenarian.%20Feeding%20and%20educating%20a%20family%20of%2040%2C%20including%20the%20couple%2C%20